												<li><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/a-first-step-toward-loving-our-enemies.html&text=<strong><em>A First Step Toward Loving Our Enemies</em></strong>&via=SoCalTaxProf"><i class="icon-twitter"></i></a></li>
												<li><a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/a-first-step-toward-loving-our-enemies.html"><i class="icon-google-plus"></i></a></li>
												<li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/a-first-step-toward-loving-our-enemies.html"><i class="icon-linkedin"></i></a></li>
