									September  5, 2020 in <a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/legal-ed-news/">Legal Ed News</a>, <a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/legal-education/">Legal Education</a>  | <a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/jobs-report-us-economy-adds-14-million-jobs-legal-profession-adds-nothing.html">Permalink</a>
									
