								<a id="a6a00d8341c4eab53ef0263e962531e200b"></a>
							
								
								<h3><a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/attorneys-for-dan-markel-murder-suspect-katherine-magbanua-seek-pretrial-release-from-prison.html"><strong><em>Attorneys For Dan Markel Murder Suspect Katherine Magbanua Seek Pretrial Release From Prison</em></strong></a></h3>
								
								
								<div class="line">
									<p class="author"> By <a href="#">Paul Caron</a></p>
									
									<div class="share hidden-phone">
										<a href="#"><i class="icon-share"></i> Share</a>
										<div class="dropdown clearfix">
											<div class="tab-arrow"></div>
											<ul class="clearfix">
												<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/attorneys-for-dan-markel-murder-suspect-katherine-magbanua-seek-pretrial-release-from-prison.html"><i class="icon-facebook"></i></a></li>
												<li><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/attorneys-for-dan-markel-murder-suspect-katherine-magbanua-seek-pretrial-release-from-prison.html&text=<strong><em>Attorneys For Dan Markel Murder Suspect Katherine Magbanua Seek Pretrial Release From Prison</em></strong>&via=SoCalTaxProf"><i class="icon-twitter"></i></a></li>
												<li><a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/attorneys-for-dan-markel-murder-suspect-katherine-magbanua-seek-pretrial-release-from-prison.html"><i class="icon-google-plus"></i></a></li>
												<li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/attorneys-for-dan-markel-murder-suspect-katherine-magbanua-seek-pretrial-release-from-prison.html"><i class="icon-linkedin"></i></a></li>
												<li><a href="mailto:?subject=<strong><em>Attorneys For Dan Markel Murder Suspect Katherine Magbanua Seek Pretrial Release From Prison</em></strong> on The Taxprof Blog&body=Check this article out on The Taxprof Blog: https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/attorneys-for-dan-markel-murder-suspect-katherine-magbanua-seek-pretrial-release-from-prison.html"><i class="icon-envelope"></i></a></li>
											</ul>
										</div>
									</div>
	
								</div>
	
								<div class="hidden-phone">
	
									<p style="text-align: justify;">Tallahassee Democrat, <a href="https://www.tallahassee.com/story/news/2020/09/03/dan-markel-murder-case-attorneys-katherine-magbanua-pretrial-release-retrial-jail-coronavirus-date/3454971001/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Attorneys for Magbanua Continue Pursuit of Pretrial Release in Dan Markel Murder Case</a>:</p>
<p style="margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #ebf0f3; line-height: 20px; color: #363636; font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;"><a class="asset-img-link" href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4eab53ef0263e96252cb200b-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="float: right;"><img alt="Magnauba" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8341c4eab53ef0263e96252cb200b img-responsive" src="https://taxprof.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4eab53ef0263e96252cb200b-250wi" style="width: 250px; margin: 0px 0px 5px 5px;" title="Magnauba" /></a>The attorneys for Dan Markel murder suspect Katherine Magbanua are again making their case to have their client released from jail on bond.</p>
<p style="margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #ebf0f3; line-height: 20px; color: #363636; font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;">They cite the October mistrial in which a jury did not convict her on charges of first-degree murder, conspiracy to commit murder or solicitation to commit first-degree murder, a lesser burden than the one required to consider whether bond is appropriate.</p>
<p style="margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #ebf0f3; line-height: 20px; color: #363636; font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;">In the 31-page filing earlier this week, Magbanua’s attorneys Chris DeCoste and Tara Kawass ask that she be released from the Leon County Detention Facility while she awaits a trial date, which is not likely until 2021. A case management conference has been set for December. ...</p>
<p style="margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #ebf0f3; line-height: 20px; color: #363636; font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;">&quot;The state’s case here rested ‘almost entirely’ on the statement of Mr. Rivera,&quot; Magbanua&#39;s attorneys wrote. &quot;It was the only piece of evidence directly implicating Ms. Magbanua… (and was) also substantially contradictory to other evidence presented at trial.&quot;</p>
<p style="margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; outline: 0px none; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: #ebf0f3; line-height: 20px; color: #363636; font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;">Their client was offered immunity in exchange for testimony against the Adelson family, which she did not give, even just days before the trial when she met with Assistant State Attorney Georgia Cappleman and State Attorney’s Office Investigator Jason Newlin. In television interviews, Cappleman alluded to the role Magbanua could play in her own release from jail.</p>

									
									<p><a class="btn btn-small" href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/attorneys-for-dan-markel-murder-suspect-katherine-magbanua-seek-pretrial-release-from-prison.html#more">Continue reading <i class="icon-double-angle-right"></i></a></p>
	
									
									
									<p class="posted">
									September  5, 2020 in <a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/legal-ed-news/">Legal Ed News</a>, <a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/legal-education/">Legal Education</a>  | <a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/attorneys-for-dan-markel-murder-suspect-katherine-magbanua-seek-pretrial-release-from-prison.html">Permalink</a>
									
