												<li><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/glogower-kamin-the-progressivity-ratchet.html&text=<strong>Glogower & Kamin: <em> The Progressivity Ratchet</em></strong>&via=SoCalTaxProf"><i class="icon-twitter"></i></a></li>
