												<li><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/black-university-of-san-diego-law-students-demand-classroom-diversity-monitors-to-report-questionabl.html&text=<strong><em>Black University Of San Diego Law Students Demand Classroom Diversity Monitors To Report ‘Questionable Conduct’</em></strong>&via=SoCalTaxProf"><i class="icon-twitter"></i></a></li>
												<li><a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/black-university-of-san-diego-law-students-demand-classroom-diversity-monitors-to-report-questionabl.html"><i class="icon-google-plus"></i></a></li>
