							<div class="article" style="border-bottom: 5px solid #00205c;">
								
								
								
	
								<a id="a6a00d8341c4eab53ef026be40e2ed0200d"></a>
							
								
								<h3><a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/applicants-sitting-for-georgia-online-bar-exam-must-sign-liability-waiver-releasing-any-potential-cl.html"><strong>Applicants Sitting For Online Georgia Bar Exam Must Sign Liability Waiver Releasing Any Potential Claims Against ExamSoft And Bar</strong></a></h3>
								
								
								<div class="line">
									<p class="author"> By <a href="#">Paul Caron</a></p>
									
									<div class="share hidden-phone">
										<a href="#"><i class="icon-share"></i> Share</a>
										<div class="dropdown clearfix">
											<div class="tab-arrow"></div>
											<ul class="clearfix">
												<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/applicants-sitting-for-georgia-online-bar-exam-must-sign-liability-waiver-releasing-any-potential-cl.html"><i class="icon-facebook"></i></a></li>
												<li><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/applicants-sitting-for-georgia-online-bar-exam-must-sign-liability-waiver-releasing-any-potential-cl.html&text=<strong>Applicants Sitting For Online Georgia Bar Exam Must Sign Liability Waiver Releasing Any Potential Claims Against ExamSoft And Bar</strong>&via=SoCalTaxProf"><i class="icon-twitter"></i></a></li>
												<li><a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/applicants-sitting-for-georgia-online-bar-exam-must-sign-liability-waiver-releasing-any-potential-cl.html"><i class="icon-google-plus"></i></a></li>
												<li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/applicants-sitting-for-georgia-online-bar-exam-must-sign-liability-waiver-releasing-any-potential-cl.html"><i class="icon-linkedin"></i></a></li>
												<li><a href="mailto:?subject=<strong>Applicants Sitting For Online Georgia Bar Exam Must Sign Liability Waiver Releasing Any Potential Claims Against ExamSoft And Bar</strong> on The Taxprof Blog&body=Check this article out on The Taxprof Blog: https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/applicants-sitting-for-georgia-online-bar-exam-must-sign-liability-waiver-releasing-any-potential-cl.html"><i class="icon-envelope"></i></a></li>
											</ul>
										</div>
									</div>
	
								</div>
	
								<div class="hidden-phone">
	
									<p>Following up on my previous posts:</p>
<ul style="text-align: justify;">
<li><a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/07/nations-first-online-bar-exam-in-michigan-crashes-examsoft-blames-cyberattack.html" rel="noopener" target="_blank"> </a><a class="asset-img-link" href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4eab53ef0263e9620ffa200b-popup" onclick="window.open( this.href, &#39;_blank&#39;, &#39;width=640,height=480,scrollbars=no,resizable=no,toolbar=no,directories=no,location=no,menubar=no,status=no,left=0,top=0&#39; ); return false" style="float: right;"><img alt="ExamSoft GA" class="asset  asset-image at-xid-6a00d8341c4eab53ef0263e9620ffa200b img-responsive" src="https://taxprof.typepad.com/.a/6a00d8341c4eab53ef0263e9620ffa200b-300wi" style="width: 300px; margin: 0px 0px 5px 5px;" title="ExamSoft GA" /></a><a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/07/nations-first-online-bar-exam-in-michigan-crashes-examsoft-blames-cyberattack.html" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Nation&#39;s First Online Bar Exam In Michigan Crashes; ExamSoft Blames Cyberattack</a> (July 29, 2020)</li>
<li><a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/08/floridas-aug-19-online-bar-exam-in-jeopardy-as-software-crashes-deans-legislators-demand-plan-b.html" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Florida&#39;s Aug. 19 Online Bar Exam In Jeopardy As Software Crashes</a>&#0160;(Aug. 15, 2020)</li>
<li><a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/08/florida-postpones-bar-exam-three-days-before-online-test-due-to-technology-failure-announces-supervi.html" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Florida Postpones Bar Exam Three Days Before Online Test Due To Technology Failure, Announces Supervised Practice Program</a>&#0160;(Aug. 17, 2020)</li>
<li><a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/08/florida-bar-exam-rescheduled-for-october-13-with-new-subjects-to-be-tested-and-new-tech-provider-app.html" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Florida Bar Exam Rescheduled For Oct. 13, With New Subjects To Be Tested And New Tech Provider; Applicants Say Prior Tech Company&#39;s Software Led To Russian Hacking Of Their Computers</a> (Aug. 29, 2020)</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Applicants planning to sit for the October 5-6 online Georgia bar exam must sign a <a href="https://twitter.com/BarExamTracker/status/1301341119700180992/photo/1" rel="noopener" target="_blank">liability waiver</a> releasing any claims they may have against ExamSoft, the Georgia bar, and the state of Georgia. The applicants also must certify that they have the &quot;experience and expertise&quot; necessary to take the exam.</p>

									
									<p><a class="btn btn-small" href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/applicants-sitting-for-georgia-online-bar-exam-must-sign-liability-waiver-releasing-any-potential-cl.html#more">Continue reading <i class="icon-double-angle-right"></i></a></p>
	
									
									
