								<a id="a6a00d8341c4eab53ef026be40dbaf6200d"></a>
							
								
								<h3><a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/university-of-florida-laura-rosenbury-is-fourth-law-school-dean-100000-neil-buchanan-is-second-tax-p.html"><strong>University Of Florida's Laura Rosenbury Is Fourth Law School Dean ($100,000), Neil Buchanan Is Second Tax Prof ($25,001) To Make Major Gifts To Students During COVID-19</strong></a></h3>
								
								
								<div class="line">
									<p class="author"> By <a href="#">Paul Caron</a></p>
									
									<div class="share hidden-phone">
										<a href="#"><i class="icon-share"></i> Share</a>
										<div class="dropdown clearfix">
											<div class="tab-arrow"></div>
