												<li><a href="mailto:?subject=<strong>University Of Florida's Laura Rosenbury Is Fourth Law School Dean ($100,000), Neil Buchanan Is Second Tax Prof ($25,001) To Make Major Gifts To Students During COVID-19</strong> on The Taxprof Blog&body=Check this article out on The Taxprof Blog: https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/university-of-florida-laura-rosenbury-is-fourth-law-school-dean-100000-neil-buchanan-is-second-tax-p.html"><i class="icon-envelope"></i></a></li>
											</ul>
