												<li><a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/wallace-presents-democratic-justice-in-tax-policymaking-today-at-nyu.html"><i class="icon-google-plus"></i></a></li>
