								<h3><a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/09/emory-law-journal-call-for-submissions-systemic-racism-in-the-law-anti-racist-solutions.html"><strong>Emory Law Journal Call For Submissions: <em> Systemic Racism In The Law & Anti-Racist Solutions</em></strong></a></h3>
								
								
								<div class="line">
									<p class="author"> By <a href="#">Paul Caron</a></p>
									
									<div class="share hidden-phone">
										<a href="#"><i class="icon-share"></i> Share</a>
