							<div class="article" style="border-bottom: 5px solid #00205c;">
								
								
								
	
								<a id="a6a00d8341c4eab53ef0263e960e078200b"></a>
							
								
								<h3><a href="https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/08/lesson-from-the-tax-court-audit-reconsideration-is-not-cdp.html"><strong>Lesson From The Tax Court: <em> Audit Reconsideration Is Not CDP</em></strong></a></h3>
								
								
								<div class="line">
									<p class="author"> By <a href="#">Bryan Camp</a></p>
									
									<div class="share hidden-phone">
