												<li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://taxprof.typepad.com/taxprof_blog/2020/08/lesson-from-the-tax-court-audit-reconsideration-is-not-cdp.html"><i class="icon-facebook"></i></a></li>
